                                "J":"<span class=\"vn\">1</span>\u00A0But God re\u00ADmem\u00ADbered Noah and all the wild an\u00ADi\u00ADmals and live\u00ADstock with him in the boat. He sent a wind to blow across the earth, and the flood\u00ADwa\u00ADters be\u00ADgan to re\u00ADcede. <a id=\"gene_8_2\"></a><span class=\"vn\">2</span>\u00A0The un\u00ADder\u00ADground wa\u00ADters stopped flow\u00ADing, and the tor\u00ADren\u00ADtial rains from the sky were stopped. <a id=\"gene_8_3\"></a><span class=\"vn\">3</span>\u00A0So the flood\u00ADwa\u00ADters grad\u00ADu\u00ADal\u00ADly re\u00ADced\u00ADed from the earth. Af\u00ADter 150\u00A0days, <a id=\"gene_8_4\"></a><span class=\"vn\">4</span>\u00A0ex\u00ADact\u00ADly five months from the time the flood be\u00ADgan,<span class=\"note_marker\"><a id=\"note_marker_33\" href=\"..%2Fnook%2FisaSample.xhtml#note_33\">[*]</a></span> the boat came to rest on the moun\u00ADtains of Ar\u00ADa\u00ADrat. <a id=\"gene_8_5\"></a><span class=\"vn\">5</span>\u00A0Two and a half months lat\u00ADer,<span class=\"note_marker\"><a id=\"note_marker_34\" href=\"..%2Fnook%2FisaSample.xhtml#note_34\">[*]</a></span> as the wa\u00ADters con\u00ADtin\u00ADued to go down, oth\u00ADer moun\u00ADtain peaks be\u00ADcame vis\u00ADi\u00ADble."
                            },
                            {  
                                "B":"#text",
                                "C":"/4/2/9",
                                "J":"\n"
                            },
                            {  
                                "B":"a",
                                "C":"/4/2/10[gene_8_6]",
                                "A":[  
                                    {  
                                        "T":"id",
                                        "d":"gene_8_6"
                                    }
                                ],
                                "J":""
                            },
                            {  
                                "B":"#text",
                                "C":"/4/2/11",
                                "J":"\n"
                            },
                            {  
                                "B":"p",
                                "C":"/4/2/12",
                                "A":[  
                                    {  
