                                ],
                                "J":"<span class=\"vn\">13</span>\u00A0Noah was now 601\u00A0years old. On the first day of the new year, ten and a half months af\u00ADter the flood be\u00ADgan,<span class=\"note_marker\"><a id=\"note_marker_35\" href=\"..%2Fnook%2FisaSample.xhtml#note_35\">[*]</a></span> the flood\u00ADwa\u00ADters had al\u00ADmost dried up from the earth. Noah lifted back the cov\u00ADer\u00ADing of the boat and saw that the sur\u00ADface of the ground was dry\u00ADing. <a id=\"gene_8_14\"></a><span class=\"vn\">14</span>\u00A0Two more months went by,<span class=\"note_marker\"><a id=\"note_marker_36\" href=\"..%2Fnook%2FisaSample.xhtml#note_36\">[*]</a></span> and at last the earth was dry!"
                            },
                            {  
                                "B":"#text",
