                                "J":"<span class=\"vn\">15</span>\u00A0Then God said to Noah, <a id=\"gene_8_16\"></a><span class=\"vn\">16</span>\u00A0\u201CLeave the boat, all of you\u2014you and your wife, and your sons and their wives. <a id=\"gene_8_17\"></a><span class=\"vn\">17</span>\u00A0Re\u00ADlease all the an\u00ADi\u00ADmals\u2014the birds, the live\u00ADstock, and the small an\u00ADi\u00ADmals that scur\u00ADry along the ground\u2014so they can be fruit\u00ADful and mul\u00ADti\u00ADply through\u00ADout the earth.\u201D"
                            },
                            {  
                                "B":"#text",
