                                    }
                                ],
                                "J":"<span class=\"vn\">18</span>\u00A0So Noah, his wife, and his sons and their wives left the boat. <a id=\"gene_8_19\"></a><span class=\"vn\">19</span>\u00A0And all of the large and small an\u00ADi\u00ADmals and birds came out of the boat, pair by pair."
                            },
                            {  
